  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一下教育平台的FastAPI应用架构。核心模块有四个：GradeSync负责成绩同步，LMS Portal是门户入口，ContentCDN处理内容分发，还有一个ClassroomService做课堂服务。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Education_LMS_Portal",
        "Education_ContentCDN",
        "Education_ClassroomService"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白。这四个都是前端入口层吗？还是分层结构？我看到GradeSync和LMS Portal名字有点像，会不会有重复？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Education_LMS_Portal"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "好问题。实际上GradeSync有两个实例——一个是用户直接访问的入口节点P，另一个是后端服务A。LMS Portal也是，PR是入口，PM是内部服务。这样设计是为了区分南北流量。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Education_LMS_Portal"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "所以GradeSync拆成P（入口）和A（服务），LMS Portal拆成PR（入口）和PM（服务），ContentCDN只有S一个节点，ClassroomService拆成C（服务）和AU（认证单元）？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "P",
        "PR",
        "S",
        "A",
        "PM",
        "C",
        "AU"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的。AU是ClassroomService的认证模块，独立出来是因为多个服务都要验证教师身份。配色上，三个入口节点P、PR、S用绿色系，服务层A、C、PM用蓝色，AU用橙色突出安全属性。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "P",
        "PR",
        "S",
        "A",
        "C",
        "PM",
        "AU"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先画FastAPI Application子图，把这八个节点放进去，按颜色分组。P、PR、S设为#82b366绿边，A、C、PM设为#6c8ebf蓝边，AU设为#d79b00橙边。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FastAPI Application",
        "P",
        "PR",
        "S",
        "A",
        "C",
        "PM",
        "AU"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "连线关系：三个入口节点P、PR、S都要连到A（GradeSync服务）和C（ClassroomService）。然后C要连PM（LMS内部服务）和AU（认证）。最后PM也要连AU做权限校验。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "P",
        "PR",
        "S",
        "A",
        "C",
        "PM",
        "AU"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "画好了。P、PR、S分别指向A和C；C指向PM和AU；PM再指向AU。这样AU有两条入边，分别是C和PM。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "P",
        "PR",
        "S",
        "A",
        "C",
        "PM",
        "AU"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等等，我发现刚才说的有问题。P、PR、S连到A和C这里，A和C应该是并列接收，但图上看起来P、PR、S是作为一个组连出去的？需要明确是分别连还是组连。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "P",
        "PR",
        "S",
        "A",
        "C"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "Mermaid里P & PR & S -- A表示三个节点各自有边指向A，不是组节点。这样符合你的设计吗？还是你想表达负载均衡的聚合关系？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "P",
        "PR",
        "S",
        "A"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "各自连线是对的，就是三个入口都能独立访问GradeSync和ClassroomService。不过A的显示名我确认下——入口P叫Education_GradeSync，但服务A也叫Education_GradeSync？这会不会混淆？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "P",
        "A"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "确实标签重复了。P和A都显示Education_GradeSync，但一个是入口网关，一个是业务服务。需要区分吗？比如P叫Education_GradeSync_Gateway？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "P",
        "A"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "不用改标签，实际代码里它们就是同名不同实例，通过上下文区分。保持现状吧。再检查下填充色——都用浅色系，P、PR、S是#d5e8d4，A、C、PM是#dae8fc，AU是#ffe6cc。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "P",
        "PR",
        "S",
        "A",
        "C",
        "PM",
        "AU"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 14,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已应用所有样式。边框宽度统一2px。我再看一眼连线：C到PM，C到AU，PM到AU——这里PM到AU是双向还是单向？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "C",
        "PM",
        "AU"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 15,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "都是单向，服务调用方向。C调用PM获取课程数据，C调用AU验证教师令牌，PM调用AU验证管理员权限。没有回调。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "C",
        "PM",
        "AU"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 16,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "完成。所有节点在FastAPI Application子图内，八节点七条边，三色分组，样式统一。需要我截图确认吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FastAPI Application"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 17,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没问题，这个结构准确反映了我们的服务拓扑。入口层绿、服务层蓝、安全模块橙，层次清晰。可以定稿了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FastAPI Application"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    }
